Show Description

From the Infowars web site ::

On the Monday, November 21 edition of the Alex Jones Show, Alex hosts from the road. 

He talks with noted trends forecaster Gerald Celente about the latest info emerging on the MF Global swindle and an article published by Forbes over the weekend accusing Celente and Jones of attempting to start a bank run by encouraging people to take their money out of banks and put it in gold and silver. 

Additional guests include Jesse Ventura, who will talk about the latest on his lawsuit against the TSA, and former trader and television host Max Keiser about the implications of the MF Global fiasco. Infowars Nightly News co-host Aaron Dykes man [sic] the Austin, Texas command center.
